data.name: Licious Clone
data.description: This is our first project at Masai School using JavaScript, HTML, and CSS.We worked on the Licious website, an online Non-Vegetarian Food selling store.

data.name: Beauty bebo clone
data.description: We cloned this website in a span of seven days. The Tech stack used is Html CSS javascript.Various UI like slideshow,login-signup, payment etc are eye-catching.javascript functionality like API, local storage, slide show with the help of set interval etc is used.
